text:
I managed to resolved the issue by myself by copying the following jars in the lib/ext folder:

Steps to resolve this issue:

1. Download standard JMeterPlugins-Standard-1.4.0.zip from http://jmeter-plugins.org/#/

2. Extract it and go inside extracted folder /lib/ext.

3. Copy JMeterPlugins-Standard.jar and CMDRunner.jar from /lib/ext to Jmeter/lib/ext
